  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A post-marketing study to look at the effects of Asmanex on markers of airway inflammation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients with asthma and not treated with anti-inflammatory medications were studied. This
      was a parallel, randomized, placebo-controlled study to investigate the effects of Asmanex on
      markers of airway inflammation including exhaled nitric oxide, airway reactivity, FEV1 and
      nitrates/nitrites and pH in exhaled breath condensate.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
